equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>J01DE51,QJ01DE51 (Combinations of antibacterials)</td></tr><tr><td>CPC (Cefepime/clavulanic acid)</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>J01DE51,QJ01DE51 (Cefepime/clavulanic acid)</td></tr><tr><td>FPE (Cefepime/enmetazobactam)</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>J01DE51,QJ01DE51 (Cefepime/enmetazobactam)</td></tr><tr><td>FNC (Cefepime/nacubactam)</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>J01DE51,QJ01DE51 (Cefepime/nacubactam)</td></tr><tr><td>FTA (Cefepime/taniborbactam)</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>J01DE51,QJ01DE51 (Cefepime/taniborbactam)</td></tr><tr><td>FPT (Cefepime/tazobactam)</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>J01DE51,QJ01DE51 (Cefepime/tazobactam)</td></tr><tr><td>FPZ (Cefepime/zidebactam)</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>J01DE51,QJ01DE51 (Cefepime/zidebactam)</td></tr><tr><td>CAT (Cefetamet)</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>J01DD10,QJ01DD10 (Other beta-lactam antibacterials)</td></tr><tr><td>FDC (Cefiderocol)</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>J01DI04,QJ01DI04 (Cefiderocol)</td></tr><tr><td>CFM (Cefixime)</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7