ide antibacterials)</td></tr><tr><td>STI (Streptomycin/isoniazid)</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>J04AM01,QJ04AM01 (Drugs for treatment of tuberculosis)</td></tr><tr><td>SUL (Sulbactam)</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>J01CG01,QJ01CG01 (Beta-lactam antibacterials, penicillins)</td></tr><tr><td>SBC (Sulbenicillin)</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>J01CA16,QJ01CA16 (Beta-lactam antibacterials, penicillins)</td></tr><tr><td>SUC (Sulconazole)</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>D01AC09,QD01AC09 (Sulconazole)</td></tr><tr><td>SUP (Sulfachlorpyridazine)</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>QJ01EQ12 (Sulfachlorpyridazine)</td></tr><tr><td>SDI (Sulfadiazine)</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>J01EC02,QJ01EQ10 (Sulfonamides and trimethoprim)</td></tr><tr><td>SLT (Sulfadiazine/tetroxoprim)</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>J01EE06 (Sulfonamides and trimethoprim)</td></tr><tr><td>SLT1 (Sulfadiazine/trimethoprim)</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>J01EE02,QJ01EW10,QJ51RE01 (Sulfonamides and trimethoprim)</td></tr><tr><td>SUD (Sulfadimethoxine)</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-rela