\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>J01CR03,QJ01CR03 (Beta-lactam antibacterials, penicillins)</td></tr><tr><td>TGC (Tigecycline)</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>J01AA12,QJ01AA12 (Tetracyclines)</td></tr><tr><td>TBQ (Tilbroquinol)</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>P01AA05 (Tilbroquinol)</td></tr><tr><td>TIP (Tildipirosin)</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>QJ01FA96 (Tildipirosin)</td></tr><tr><td>TIL (Tilmicosin)</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>QJ01FA91 (Tilmicosin)</td></tr><tr><td>TIN (Tinidazole)</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>G01AF21,J01XD02,P01AB02,QG01AF21,QJ01XD02,QP51AA02 (Other antibacterials)</td></tr><tr><td>TCR (Tiocarlide)</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>J04AD02,QJ04AD02 (Drugs for treatment of tuberculosis)</td></tr><tr><td>TOB (Tobramycin)</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>J01GB01,QJ01GB01,QS01AA12,S01AA12 (Aminoglycoside antibacterials)</td></tr><tr><td>TFX (Tosufloxacin)</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>J01MA22,QJ01MA22,QS01AE09,S01AE09 (Tosufloxacin)</td></tr><tr><td>TMP (Trimethoprim)</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equiva